patch.description:
Required permission &lt;b&gt;NAMESPACE:{namespace}:USER:{userId}:CONTENT:SHARECODE [UPDATE]&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;br&gt;
					This endpoint is used to modify the shareCode of a content. However, this operation is restricted by default and requires the above permission to be granted to the User role.&lt;br&gt;
					&lt;code&gt;shareCode&lt;/code&gt; format should follows:
					Max length: 7
					Available characters: abcdefhkpqrstuxyz

